Page_0: "I've heard rumors of bandits hiding out in the sewers. Bah... that's almost as crazy as that old taffer Rupert who claims he saw a burrick down there. Burricks? Bandits? Well whatever it is, I'm going down there to prove myself to Lady MacAlpine. No longer will she just see me as a smelly fisherman. Nope. I'm going to be an adventurer. Yep ... they always get the wimmin.


- Big Willy The Adventurer"